{{Eastern Slavic name|Mikhailovich|Volkov}} {{Expand Russian|Волков, Леонид Михайлович (политик)|date=August 2018}} {{Infobox officeholder | honorific-prefix = | name = Leonid Volkov | native_name = Леонид Волков | native_name_lang = ru | image = File:Леонид Волков на забастовке избирателей близкое фото.jpg | image_size = | image_upright = | birth_name = Leonid Mikhailovich Volkov | birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1980|11|10}} | birth_place = [[Yekaterinburg|Sverdlovsk]], [[Sverdlovsk Oblast]], [[Russian SFSR]], [[USSR]] | citizenship = | nationality = {{flag|Russia}}n | party = [[Progress Party (Russia)|Progress Party]] | relatives = | residence = | education = | alma_mater = [[Ural State University]] | occupation = Politician | profession = | website = [https://www.leonidvolkov.ru/ www.leonidvolkov.ru] }} '''Leonid Mikhailovich Volkov''' ({{lang-ru|Леони́д Миха́йлович Во́лков}}; born 10 November 1980, [[Yekaterinburg|Sverdlovsk]], [[Sverdlovsk Oblast]], [[USSR]]) is a [[Russian people|Russian]] politician of the unregistered [[Progress Party (Russia)|Progress Party]], member of the [[Russian opposition]], and chief of staff for [[Alexei Navalny]]'s [[Alexei Navalny presidential campaign, 2018|campaign]] for the [[Russian presidential election, 2018|2018 presidential election]]. He is also a former deputy of the [[Yekaterinburg]] City Duma.
Volkov was a member of the central election committee of the [[Russian Opposition Coordination Council]] and was one of the leaders of Navalny's [[Alexei Navalny mayoral campaign, 2013|2013 mayoral campaign]] for [[Moscow]].<ref>[http://lenta.ru/news/2012/06/26/party/ Политика: Соратники Навального создадут партию без него]. Lenta. Published 26 July 2012. Retrieved 3 May 2017. {{ru icon}}</ref><ref>[http://lenta.ru/articles/2012/08/06/electronicperformers/ Lenta.ru: Политика: Электронная партия]. Published 6 August 2012. Retrieved 3 May 207. {{ru icon}}</ref> He was formerly a member of the political council of the [[People's Freedom Party]].<ref>[http://leonwolf.livejournal.com/395819.html О всякой всячине — Дела партийные (и личные тоже)] {{ru icon}}</ref> Since December 2016, Volkov has been a chief of staff by [[Alexei Navalny presidential campaign, 2018|Alexey Navalny presidential campaign]].
